{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dohd man mannas See-\nwäs un mannuß Behrnus/ kadeht\nes tew kalpojis eſinu / tad es ee-\nschu / jo tu gann finni to Kalpo-\nfchami/ar fo es tew eſimu kalpojis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lahbans fazztja us to:\nJa es luhdsans/ Schehlastibu ef-\nmu atraddis tawäs Azzis/ es eſ-\nnu noprattis / ka tas KUNGS\nmann tewis deht irr fivehtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja winſch : praf-\nfi to Algu / tad es to dohfchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazztja us winnu :\ntu finni/ ka'es tew eſimu kalpojis/\nun ka tawi Lohpi pee man irr\nbijufchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo preeſſch mannim tew\nbij Maggums / un tas irr leetä\nPulka wairojees / un tas\nKUNGS irr tew fivehtijs zaur\nmannu Kahju / un nu / kad buhs\ntad man favu Nammu apgah-\ndahf?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winſch fazztja : ko es\ntew dohfchu? tad fazztja Jehkabs/\ntew ne buhs man ne neela doht/ ja\ntu man fcho Leetu darrifi/ tad es\natkaf gannifchn/un jargafchu ta-\nwas Awis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es iſſtaigafchu ſchodeen\npa wiﬀu tawn Gannamn-Pul-\nku / un atſchkirſchu no turrenes\nwiſſus raibus/ un lahfainus Loh-\npus / un wiſſus mellus Lohpus\nstarp teem Jehreem / un wiſſus\nlahfainus/ un raibus/starp tahm\nRasahm / un tahs buhs man par\nAlgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad athudehs man-\nſniba/ jeb ſchodeen jeb riht\ntu nahſſi pahr mannu Al-\npreeſſch tawahn Azzim /\nkas ne irr raibs / un lah-\nstarp tahm Rasahm / un\nstarp teem Jehreem / to b\nes ſadsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazztja La-\nRedſi / Mannis pehz lai\npehz tawu Wahrdü.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas atſchkihre\nDeenä tohs lahfainus/ un\nAhſchus/ un wiſſas lahfaix-\nraibas Kasas/ wiſſu/ pee k-\ntuns bija/ un wiſſ / ka-\nbija / starp teem Jehreen\nwinſch eedewe tohs favo\nnu Rohkä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fchkihrahs trejo\nGahjumu starp few un\nJehkabn / un Jehkabs g\nLahbana zittas Awis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Jehkab-\nſtes no falkeem Peppekeen\nLasda-Kohkeem/un Kastan-\nkeem / un rohbija eekſch te-\ntus Rohbus / nomisoda\nBaltumu / kas wirs tahm\nstehm bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winſch likke tob\nzinus / ko winſch bij miſc-\ndens-Sillês/un Dſerama-\nkös tahm Awim preeſſcha/\ndſert nahfdamas apetohs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs Awis apg\npahr tahm Rihſtehm / u-\ndahs eeraibas / lahfaixa-\nraibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs atſchkih\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
